lank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170206/s00002/1486317885001</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 一名律師駕駛跑車至香港仔時失控撞毀十米鐵欄後車輛翻轉，全車嚴重損毀，司機與車中一名乘客事後截的士離開。乘客自行到醫院求醫，駕車司機則返家五小時後再到警署自首，其涉酒後駕駛被捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170206/s00002/1486317890337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170206%2Fs00002%2F1486317890337&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c2abea0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170206%2Fs00002%2F1486317890337&h=3d80a0fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170206/s00002/1486317890337</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170206/00176_032.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170206%2F00176_032.html&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e8925e41\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170206/00176_032.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1545078&amp;target=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1545078%26target%3D2&d=K4UaoR%2Bzp7qM8XPwf0LBI4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b17ed5d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Fdaily%2Fnews-content.php%3Fid%3D1545078%26target%3D2&h=2c4e7a91\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/daily/news-content.php?id=1545078&amp;target=2</a> (星島日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 屯門樂翠街青山別墅怡景閣地下一單位發生爆竊案，女戶主返家時發現大門被人反鎖，其召鎖匠前來開門後發現屋內有被人搜掠痕迹，窗戶亦遭撬毀，懷疑遭賊人爆竊，其已報警求助。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170206/00176_033.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%